originalText.text: My daughter was here for 2 years, Miss Debra is amazing teacher, but after my daughter pass to the next class, things changed, she had this one accident there, my daughter hit herself with the door, it was bad, my daughter complain for this having pain there, when I took her to ER, the hospital asked me for a report of this accident, I didn’t have anything, they also didn’t call me when that happened, I found out when I arrived, also some people there don’t have patience with the kids. Honestly I think you can get a better place for your child.
